prompt.title: Embedding for AI-Friendly Book Language Markup
prompt.content: The Book language is a human-understandable markup language for writing AI applications such as chatbots, knowledge bases, agents, avatars, translators, and automations. It is based on markdown and designed to be easily readable and writable.
